The '''DZFoot d'Or''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] award, created in 2000 by the [[Algeria]]n football website DZFoot.com, the leading source of Algerian football news. The award is given annually to the [[Algeria]]n player considered to have performed the best over the previous year.
==DZFoot d'Or Winners==
