'''''{{Nihongo|T.E. Lawrence|TEロレンス|TE Rorensu}}''''' is a ''[[shōnen-ai]]'' [[manga]] by {{Nihongo|Tomoko Kosaka|神坂智子|Kosaka Tomoko}} loosely based on the life of [[T. E. Lawrence]]. It first appeared in ''[[Wings (manga magazine)|Wings]]'' magazine from November 1984-November 1988.
